{"tid":1144692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(地球經濟中心) 外媒隨機街訪深圳民眾：沒聽說美國將加關稅","createTime":"2019-05-08T08:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T22:49:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a473c55fd484f52c1b41688d234bc898e7712424","tid":1144692,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"美中貿易戰打得火熱，在雙方談判進入最後階段之際，川普揚言將向2000億中國商品商品加稅，引起全球關注，外媒實際走訪中國南方經濟中心「深圳」，但隨機詢問路人，對方不是沒聽說川普加稅，就是透過「非官方管道」獲悉此事，情況相當詭異。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》週二（7日）在深圳進行隨機街訪，路人對於川普將加稅一事似乎不太清楚，有人認為中國股市6日大跌是因為美國加稅影響，但也有人對中國今後經濟情勢表達樂觀。而深圳的人力市場附近有年輕人終日遊蕩，因為沒有專業，找不到滿意的工作，也不願意去工廠做高強度的勞動，只好泡在網咖裡，缺錢時再出來打工。<br />\n<br />\n1名中興通訊招聘員工的仲介則說，中興的招聘已經結束，具體訊息是公司機密無法透露；1名富士康工人透露，工廠流動性很大，薪水主要靠加班撐起，但他不清楚廠裡有沒有中共黨組織，但有工會維護工人權益。<br />\n<br />\n1名餐廳老闆則說，富士康去年開始大批裁員，導致餐廳業績受到影響，而1年前附近的網咖座無虛席，幾乎都是富士康員工光顧，如今卻是冷冷清清，有些網咖還關門大吉。但報導也稱，有看到富士康成都廠區的招聘訊息。深圳中泰科技園1名負責對外聯絡的人士表示，美國對中國出口產品加稅，將給對美國出口量大的廠商造成較大影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2783515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2783515&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=72f290b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2783515&h=8d7d298c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2783515</a>"},{"pid":"5a49d1c7183ea082dada721b54a0001c7e3fb581","tid":1144692,"uid":152476,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0ca268669db3715fb9b67b4f85d8ad3f749dec","tid":1144692,"uid":249885,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"牆的意義 盡在支那"},{"pid":"8bf00f33143322767198e89dd388107f79e5cfb4","tid":1144692,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb65e96d52ebdca3121a10e52a302a11289b4db9","tid":1144692,"uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"一國兩制之要義"},{"pid":"0c659a3d298e9c263fea561e45b4454ed848f2e4","tid":1144692,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9d2fe891863c6f18a8caf413893d4d108e9100","tid":1144692,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b824faeeae1ca5a5de67bc3c29ad4a231bdd96cd","tid":1144692,"uid":217761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9f9d2fe891863c6f18a8caf413893d4d108e9100","tid":1144692,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"支那人可以食草了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba61590173958048dd1004c8a668b28bfc3f54a9","tid":1144692,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"拎支那人既錢填<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da49c6a3a0ff2f2f4cbd945491962c59285838aa","tid":1144692,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T22:09:31.000Z","msg":"飲住咖啡睇你班支那狗就死都唔知係幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2857ec769ad45246b81b8ab79edd455a8ca022","tid":1144692,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT